OL,5, Some trainee doctors and consultants at
OL,6, one Welsh health board are "scared to  
OL,7, come to work", a report has found.     
OL,9,FA report by the Royal College of       
OL,10,FPhysicians (RCP) described "frightening
OL,11,Fexperiences" staff faced at Aneurin    
OL,12,FBevan University Health Board.         
OL,14,FChronic understaffing and excessive    
OL,15,Fworkloads at the Grange hospital in    
OL,16,FCwmbran were causing "very serious     
OL,17,Fpatient safety concerns", it added.    
OL,19,FThe Health Board said it had taken the 
OL,20,Ffindings of the report very seriously. 
